Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.60,0:00:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡萊多劇團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.90,0:00:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的表演既不是馬戲 也不是音樂劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.40,0:00:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不是魔術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.19,0:00:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是世界第一的娛樂表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.70,0:00:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一位少女憧憬于那樣的舞臺而挑戰舞臺的主角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.50,0:00:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苗木野•空 16歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.00,0:00:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那夢想的舞臺因某人而被奪走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.40,0:00:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空她們能夠奪回卡萊多嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.00,0:02:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是夫魯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.10,0:02:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有被舞臺選中的人才能見得到的舞臺精靈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.30,0:02:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 苗木野•空是唯一一個能看見我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.30,0:02:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她以天生的毅力和努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.00,0:02:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踏實的登上通往明星的臺階
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.19,0:02:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於實現和嚮往已久的超級明星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.00,0:02:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉一起登臺表演的夢想了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.60,0:02:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但表演正精彩激烈的期間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.90,0:02:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前所未有的試煉降臨在空她們的身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.30,0:02:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的卡萊多劇團在今天的演出之後就解散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.80,0:02:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡萊多劇團要……解散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.90,0:03:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不禁讓人懷疑自己的耳朵的事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.90,0:03:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直順利的卡萊多劇團突然被收購
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.40,0:03:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到今天為止即將被解散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.30,0:03:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個幕後黑手正是由利•其力安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.50,0:03:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與蕾拉人氣相同的卡萊多劇團的招牌明星的他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.40,0:03:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密的進行著奪取計畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.80,0:03:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我贏了…贏了卡洛斯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.60,0:03:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最後的演出前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.40,0:03:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空想把自己對舞臺的思念之情告訴卡洛斯 但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.00,0:03:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然今晚是最後一場表演了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.90,0:03:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也正因為是最後一場表演了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.80,0:03:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家決定盡最大的努力\N把最好的一場表演奉獻給觀眾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.10,0:03:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆你有沒有什麼想對大家說的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.80,0:03:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要說的只有一句話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.20,0:03:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你們這麼想的話 那還不如不去表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.70,0:03:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為卡洛斯冷言相對而動搖的空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.70,0:03:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於連我的身姿都看不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.30,0:04:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫魯…夫魯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.20,0:04:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 夫魯 我有事想問你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.20,0:04:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫魯 回答我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.40,0:04:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.60,0:04:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看不見夫魯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.70,0:04:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看見我就說明你是被舞臺所選中的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.70,0:04:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經有個男人能看見我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.70,0:04:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而他漸漸的看不見我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.80,0:04:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都失去 窮途沒落的空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.60,0:04:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦好 已經完全糊塗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.30,0:04:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而斬斷她煩惱的是卻是蕾拉的一番出乎意料的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.80,0:04:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論再怎麼努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.70,0:04:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的卡萊多劇團今天是最後一場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.39,0:04:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可從來沒認為這是最後一場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.30,0:04:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.39,0:04:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 正視現實吧 蕾拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.89,0:04:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你要整垮卡萊多劇團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.30,0:05:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也無法阻止我追求我的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.60,0:05:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我沒有追尋到自己的未來之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.60,0:05:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不會表演自己的最後一場演出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.00,0:05:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我有一點點不能堅持這種信念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.89,0:05:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就無法站在這個舞臺上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.20,0:05:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.20,0:05:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不會就這麼結束的對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.89,0:05:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天開始我要和蕾拉小姐一起更加更加……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.30,0:05:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空 快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.90,0:05:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幕會準時拉開的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.20,0:05:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.30,0:05:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能我只是不想失去而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.80,0:05:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去能讓我這麼熱血沸騰的搭檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.30,0:05:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.60,0:05:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.80,0:05:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才弄花妝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.00,0:05:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在補妝呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.40,0:05:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.30,0:05:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.20,0:05:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我很快就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.80,0:06:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.50,0:06:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫你補吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.80,0:06:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.40,0:06:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.90,0:06:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會化不好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.40,0:06:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.90,0:06:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你一起表演很開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.30,0:06:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐 為什麼說這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.90,0:06:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會就這麼結束的對嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.40,0:06:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.50,0:06:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.20,0:06:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.20,0:06:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫魯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.50,0:06:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又再次看得見…我了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.00,0:06:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 有點遺憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.30,0:06:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『太陽』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.60,0:06:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張卡的意思是“邁向明天的希望”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.60,0:06:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“邁向明天的希望”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.20,0:06:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.00,0:07:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 明天起就是我們新舞臺的開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.60,0:07:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣 拉下了各懷思念的一幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.20,0:07:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,團員們各自走向了他們自己的道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.30,0:07:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日子過的真快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.60,0:07:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想再一次在那華麗的舞臺上大放光彩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.80,0:07:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼想的他們 勤奮的自修練習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.70,0:07:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有努力的打工生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.90,0:07:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 給 給
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.00,0:07:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面 蕾拉她依照父親的意思參加了電影的拍攝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.90,0:07:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.40,0:07:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各自度過著新的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.30,0:07:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天 機會降臨到空她們的身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.50,0:07:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給你們帶來工作了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.20,0:07:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.60,0:07:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬林遊樂園的戶外舞臺招聘出演者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.10,0:07:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,規模雖小 但能再次站在舞臺上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.50,0:08:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mail有回信了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.30,0:08:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.30,0:08:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家說都會來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.30,0:08:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾你們啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.50,0:08:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.40,0:08:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣 過去的夥伴再次集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.10,0:08:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新組合FREEDOMRIZE結成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.20,0:08:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著在表演的當日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.80,0:08:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消除了壓抑已久的鬱悶的空他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.80,0:08:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表現出了非常出色的表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.70,0:08:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演出以盛況空前的形式下結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.70,0:08:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好像有什麼不足…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.20,0:08:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這時蕾拉小姐在的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.29,0:08:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這樣想的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.40,0:08:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.70,0:08:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.50,0:08:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.79,0:08:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由翱翔在天空的謎之面具明星登場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.20,0:08:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展現了壓倒性的表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.90,0:09:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.40,0:09:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 一下子就吸引了全場觀眾的目光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.10,0:09:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於謎之面具明星的活躍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.29,0:09:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬林遊樂園連續幾日遊客暴滿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.20,0:09:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空他們的表演也受到了好評
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.60,0:09:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那一天 事故發生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.70,0:09:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 攝影師 別拍漏了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.60,0:09:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.40,0:09:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是面具明星啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.00,0:09:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了清楚的看表演的幼小的兄妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.40,0:09:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爬上了鐵塔梯子的高處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.50,0:09:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那兩個孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.20,0:09:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻聯繫救援人員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.40,0:09:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美莉莎 你先走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.20,0:09:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.79,0:10:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種熟練的身姿一定是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.79,0:10:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空確信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.70,0:10:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.10,0:10:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 要撞上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.50,0:10:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好抓緊我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.40,0:10:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.10,0:10:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與面具明星的合作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.10,0:10:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算擺脫危機的空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.90,0:10:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信 面具明星一定是蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.90,0:11:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐和我們在一起的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.40,0:11:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創造出我們的卡萊多劇團也不是問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.70,0:11:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.10,0:11:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由利的魔手又一次伸向了空她們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.70,0:11:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後終於…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.50,0:11:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面具明星的真面目被揭開了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.70,0:11:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於由利妨礙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.40,0:11:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被馬林遊樂園炒魷魚的空她們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.40,0:11:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賭上唯一的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.20,0:11:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加了溫哥華國際表演大賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.80,0:11:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.70,0:11:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在這裏受到好評
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.10,0:11:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬林遊樂園的老闆會重新考慮也說不定啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.00,0:11:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面 蕾拉在倫敦的電影拍攝正在順利的進行著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.50,0:11:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.70,0:11:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍攝順利是首要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.70,0:11:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這部電影是否成功對你將來的影響非常大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.51,0:11:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.00,0:11:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下週末影片將進入最高潮的拍攝期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.80,0:11:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預祝你成功 蕾拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.00,0:11:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.60,0:12:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後在比賽當日…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.30,0:12:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這算什麼?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.10,0:12:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Z?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.70,0:12:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待著空FREEDOMRIZE她們的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.90,0:12:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相同表演內容的本地街頭表演小組Z
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.10,0:12:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.60,0:12:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們的不是一模一樣嘛?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.10,0:12:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被盜取了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.80,0:12:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 這又是由利的計謀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.80,0:12:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能阻止這棵好苗苗的成長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.70,0:12:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成的太漂亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.40,0:12:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能夠向這種傢伙認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.60,0:12:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在表演之前 被逼上絕路FREEDOMRIZE…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.90,0:12:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.40,0:12:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.70,0:12:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我知道了 攝影延期至下周吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.90,0:13:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相應的我期待你的最佳表現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.90,0:13:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現的是謎之面具明星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.60,0:13:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 空她們的表演開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.50,0:13:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面具明星!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.80,0:13:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道你自己在幹什麼嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.60,0:14:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在誰都確信FREEDOMRIZE將獲得優勝的時候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.50,0:14:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別來妨礙我的好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.10,0:14:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.50,0:14:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.10,0:14:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天應該是拍攝影片的高潮幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.80,0:14:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經申請延期拍攝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.40,0:14:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.10,0:14:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我這麼做很任性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.60,0:14:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不能不這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.70,0:14:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想完整地…完整地演出場燃盡熱情的表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.60,0:14:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想揮灑身體中更多的激情的汗水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.00,0:15:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在對我來說就是她們的夥伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.00,0:15:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.70,0:15:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒有表演我的最後一場演出呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.80,0:15:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 影片一定要拍完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.10,0:15:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後就隨你便吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.80,0:15:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和空她們一起重新登臺演出下定決心的蕾拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.70,0:15:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她身上發生了奇跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.10,0:15:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得見…我了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.90,0:15:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 下定決心登臺表演的她也終於看得見我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.40,0:15:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉現在已被舞臺選中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.40,0:15:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那正是能夠挑戰“夢幻超絕技”的證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.50,0:15:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“夢幻超絕技”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.70,0:15:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經有人挑戰過一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.40,0:16:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就再也沒有成功過的絕技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.40,0:16:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的人過於害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.40,0:16:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的人勉強挑戰而喪失性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.00,0:16:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想要挑戰的話 需要卡萊多劇團的二人組
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.00,0:16:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑戰“夢幻超絕技”需要二位元明星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.50,0:16:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前失敗的那二個人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.50,0:16:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.60,0:16:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我覺得和蕾拉小姐一起就可以成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.80,0:16:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下定決心的二人前往的是特訓的舞臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.30,0:16:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布蘭得峽谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.10,0:16:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那等待她們的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.60,0:16:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一知道“夢幻超絕技”的一個人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.90,0:16:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.80,0:16:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.30,0:16:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,團長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.00,0:16:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好思想準備了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.90,0:16:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 空和蕾拉殘酷的特訓開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.00,0:17:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連續幾日的訓練遠遠超過了她們所想像的難度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.30,0:17:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對踏實完成課題的蕾拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.50,0:17:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空光是跟上蕾拉就已經竭盡全力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.58,0:17:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.70,0:17:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐 為什麼什麼都不對我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.58,0:17:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請說些什麼 無論什麼都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.40,0:17:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒什麼要說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.80,0:17:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去對搭檔信任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.00,0:17:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被蕾拉冷言相對而決心動搖的空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.30,0:17:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半吊子的覺悟只會給人添麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.80,0:17:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我退出是為了蕾拉的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.30,0:18:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去自信的空下定決心向著蕾拉的房間走去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.08,0:18:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐 我有話想對你說 蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.00,0:18:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.00,0:18:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐現在不在房間裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.50,0:18:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去長跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.08,0:18:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長跑 在這種時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.50,0:18:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 在減肥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.58,0:18:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,減肥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.08,0:18:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 可能是兩個人的體重差越大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.30,0:18:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“夢幻超絕技”的成功率就越低
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.50,0:18:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我害的 讓蕾拉小姐做這樣的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.90,0:18:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為搭檔是相等的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.90,0:18:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.00,0:18:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.58,0:18:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.40,0:18:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我竟然想逃避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.20,0:18:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特訓又累又苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.50,0:19:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以覺得自己沒有成為蕾拉的搭檔的實力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.08,0:19:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只想著一個人逃避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.20,0:19:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我不會再迷茫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.70,0:19:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會更加地更加地努力 趕上你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.08,0:19:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定讓“夢幻超絕技”成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.90,0:19:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就是為了這個才來這裏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.20,0:19:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.00,0:19:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢復信賴關係的空和蕾拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.30,0:19:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是神又賦予了她們更大的試煉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.30,0:19:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.58,0:19:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過度減肥而神智不清的蕾拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.90,0:19:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.70,0:19:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 好像沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.40,0:20:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受傷的蕾拉 等待這二人殘酷的命運究竟是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.70,0:20:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於 展現特訓的成果的時刻到來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.40,0:20:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不慎撞上懸崖的身體狀況惡化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.70,0:20:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發展到醫生建議修養的事態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.58,0:20:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而她的決意卻毫不動搖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.40,0:20:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時候成熟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.20,0:20:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跨越殘酷的試煉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.08,0:20:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空和蕾拉終於要挑戰“夢幻超絕技”了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.20,0:20:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒系安全帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.08,0:20:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像心跳加速了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.40,0:20:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要過去了 空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.20,0:20:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.30,0:20:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只看著蕾拉小姐一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.30,0:21:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.50,0:21:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去到蕾拉小姐的身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.08,0:21:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的背上長有翅膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.08,0:21:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.08,0:21:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為和蕾拉小姐在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.70,0:21:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好幸福的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.30,0:21:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感動的快流淚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.70,0:21:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但願一直這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.20,0:21:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.90,0:21:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展現其生命的璀璨光輝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.00,0:21:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那正是“夢幻超絕技”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.60,0:21:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不僅僅是單純的危險技能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.70,0:21:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越接近死亡越淡漠死亡 表現出強烈的生命力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.50,0:21:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 還有 盡可能的將這種生命力傳遞給觀眾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.60,0:21:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是夢幻的超絕技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.60,0:21:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大膽地去吧
